snippet.title: The Scoop [12.20.19] Featured Guest: Amber Anderson
snippet.description:
The newest edition of The Scoop featuring Amber Anderson, a top producer in the San Diego Real Estate Market is out!! In this edition, you’ll hear about the latest market trends, along with some great tools to use for your business. You’ll also hear from Mark Marquez, one of our past board presidents, and Mike Mercurio, our San Diego MLS and San Diego Association of REALTORS® CEO! 

This is just one of the many resources we offer our members and the San Diego market, as the premier, local MLS provider. We know that market updates and the latest information for real estate activity are valuable to your business, and we strive to provide the best tools and resources in San Diego!
